item.title: About me
item.description: Hi there! My name is Sean and you've stumbled across my blog. I'll be mostly posting about my side projects and things that I have learnt or find to be interesting. I don't presume to be an expert on anything, but I do enjoy my work. My interests predominantly lie in the practical application of statistics/machine learning to aid in decision making or for the creation of data-driven products. Feel free to reach out to me on LinkedIn if you would like to connect.
